node.text: Mainly what I want you guys to take from this video is there’s no special secret to weight loss. It takes time, effort, and consistency. Eating healthy is the BEST & FASTEST way to lose weight & not eating 3-4 hours before you go to bed or eating extremely light like applesauce: I’ve recently found myself cutting meat and slowly cutting dairy products. Question I get a lot “How do you not eat crazy when you get the munchies” and it’s because I don’t even buy the crazy shit anymore & BEING HIGH HEALTHY SHIT TASTE GOOD! Get high af and eat a Caesar salad. That shit go off! 😂❤️ but for tho just try eating better snacks like granola, apples & peanut butter, celery & ranch. While y’all saying y’all can’t do it, y’all coulda dropped 20 pounds by now. START YOUR JOURNEY TODAY!
